        "timestamp": "2017-09-21 01:43:56.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nIs there a good reason for skipping Sonar for this project?\n\nZhaoxing: Since Sonar doesn't support the coverage Analytics for Python project, I'd like to remove this project from Sonar.\n\nWhy are we removing the verify python job?\n\nZhaoxing: The verify job failed due to  toxini.ini not found error, actually this file exist but in the directory \"nfvparser\\src\\main\\python\" instead of the root directory, can I change the jjb configuration to point to this file to nfvparser\\src\\main\\python\\toxini.ini\"\n22:28:23 ERROR: toxini file 'tox.ini' not found\n22:28:23 Build step 'Execute shell' marked build as failure",
